{"tid":997430,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泫雅、E’dawn簽給新公司！","createTime":"2019-01-27T07:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T23:04:08.000Z","uid":74065,"like":216,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"ce116c8f66f9081e0363d9237e18d2a000ab1083","tid":997430,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T07:24:42.000Z","msg":"南韓甜蜜情侶檔泫雅、E&rsquo;dawn於2018年認愛交往2年，兩人為愛抗爭，最後演變成雙雙離開經紀公司Cube娛樂，其中一度傳聞泫雅將簽給嘻哈品牌公司AOMG，但最後證實沒有。情侶倆在度過近4個月沒有公司打理的狀況下，終於在27日找到歸屬，韓媒爆料，他們一併簽給PSY，成為經紀公司P NATION旗下藝人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3865/d3865867.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3865%2Fd3865867.jpg&h=d69a4521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泫雅、E&rsquo;dawn簽給PSY。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3865/d3865868.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3865%2Fd3865868.jpg&h=0fba578d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲泫雅、E&rsquo;dawn蓋章簽約照公開。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\nPSY因一曲《江南Style》躍升成為國際巨星，他2018年離開YG娛樂後，於2019年自立門戶，創立經紀公司P NATION，第一位簽下的藝人就是個人魅力十足的Jessi，27日再傳來好消息，泫雅、E&rsquo;dawn也投入PSY的懷抱裡，成為公司第二組藝人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3865/d3865866.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3865%2Fd3865866.jpg&h=1a3045bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲PSY自立門戶，第一個藝人就簽Jessi。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPSY於官方Instagram貼出泫雅、E&rsquo;dawn手指蓋章的認證照，間接透露兩人未來的去路。事實上，泫雅、E&rsquo;dawn這幾個月雖沒有所屬公司，但兩人依舊在樂壇裡努力不懈，創作、舞蹈練習都沒懈怠，如今找到好歸宿，粉絲也很開心，更有部分網友跪求「可不可以一起簽2ne1」。"},{"pid":"76dfb2f9298d8e3093af77b614e6bacf8c5ff33a","tid":997430,"uid":171594,"like":391,"dislike":1,"score":390,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T07:27:44.000Z","msg":"原來連psy都走咗<br />\nBigbang遲吓完約走埋 YG係咪可以宣佈摺埋"},{"pid":"d13d9440490c61352888e4600cbe23a95c5021be","tid":997430,"uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":36,"score":-32,"quote":{"pid":"76dfb2f9298d8e3093af77b614e6bacf8c5ff33a","tid":997430,"uid":17159